WEBVTT

00:01.209 --> 00:03.089
<i>Previously on Mad Men...</i>

00:03.577 --> 00:04.548
Heaven's a little morbid.

00:04.665 --> 00:05.679
I didn't get to Heaven.

00:05.770 --> 00:07.233
Something terrible
has to happen.

00:07.379 --> 00:09.783
I'm sorry my accomplishments
happen in broad daylight

00:09.877 --> 00:11.930
and I can't be given
the same rewards.

00:12.654 --> 00:13.950
I'm sorry, but your
name escapes me.

00:14.059 --> 00:16.918
I'm Bob Benson.
I'm upstairs, in Accounts.

00:17.055 --> 00:18.997
You know,
but just in the outfield.

00:19.282 --> 00:20.304
What did they say?

00:20.479 --> 00:22.502
It's just like last time, no.

00:22.611 --> 00:24.435
We cannot go on like this.

00:24.528 --> 00:26.653
This is what Chevy
is paying us for.

00:26.759 --> 00:28.330
It's not our clock,
it's theirs.

00:28.416 --> 00:29.828
So what's another weekend?

